            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Perhaps this could work, given all extensions above are added to `vim.filetype` matching:\r\n\r\n```lua\r\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd('BufReadPre', {\r\n  callback = function(ev)\r\n    local ft = vim.filetype.match({ filename = ev.file })\r\n    if ft == 'zip' then\r\n      vim.api.nvim_create_autocmd('BufReadCmd', {\r\n        once = true,\r\n        callback = function(ev2)\r\n          require('nvim.archive').open_listing(ev2.buf, ev2.file)\r\n        end,\r\n      })\r\n    end\r\n  end,\r\n})\r\n```",
            "commit_id": "b29aedcc7a444187400d7367115d57beec915f52",
            "created_at": "2026-04-20T13:59:45Z",
